verses.text_plain: O give thanks unto the Lord; for he is good: for his mercy endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html: 1O give thanks unto the Lord; for he is good: for his mercy endureth for ever.

verses.text_plain: O give thanks unto the God of gods: for his mercy endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html: 2O give thanks unto the God of gods: for his mercy endureth for ever.

verses.text_plain: O give thanks to the Lord of lords: for his mercy endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html: 3O give thanks to the Lord of lords: for his mercy endureth for ever.

verses.text_plain: To him who alone doeth great wonders: for his mercy endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html: 4To him who alone doeth great wonders: for his mercy endureth for ever.

verses.text_plain: To him that by wisdom made the heavens: for his mercy endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html: 5To him that by wisdom made the heavens: for his mercy endureth for ever.

verses.text_plain: To him that stretched out the earth above the waters: for his mercy endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html: 6To him that stretched out the earth above the waters: for his mercy endureth for ever.

verses.text_plain: To him that made great lights: for his mercy endureth for ever:
verses.verse_html: 7To him that made great lights: for his mercy endureth for ever:

verses.text_plain: The sun to rule by day: for his mercy endureth for ever:
verses.verse_html:
8The sun to rule by day: for his mercy endureth for ever: ▼
▼ to rule…: Heb. for the rulings by day

footnotes.body_text: ▼ to rule…: Heb. for the rulings by day
footnotes.body_html: ▼ to rule…: Heb. for the rulings by day

verses.text_plain: The moon and stars to rule by night: for his mercy endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html: 9The moon and stars to rule by night: for his mercy endureth for ever.

verses.text_plain: To him that smote Egypt in their firstborn: for his mercy endureth for ever:
verses.verse_html: 10To him that smote Egypt in their firstborn: for his mercy endureth for ever:

verses.text_plain: And brought out Israel from among them: for his mercy endureth for ever:
verses.verse_html: 11And brought out Israel from among them: for his mercy endureth for ever:

verses.text_plain: With a strong hand, and with a stretched out arm: for his mercy endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html: 12With a strong hand, and with a stretched out arm: for his mercy endureth for ever.

verses.text_plain: To him which divided the Red sea into parts: for his mercy endureth for ever:
verses.verse_html: 13To him which divided the Red sea into parts: for his mercy endureth for ever:

verses.text_plain: And made Israel to pass through the midst of it: for his mercy endureth for ever:
verses.verse_html: 14And made Israel to pass through the midst of it: for his mercy endureth for ever:

verses.text_plain: But overthrew Pharaoh and his host in the Red sea: for his mercy endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html:
15But overthrew Pharaoh and his host in the Red sea: for his mercy endureth for ever. ▼
▼ overthrew: Heb. shaked off

footnotes.body_html: ▼ overthrew: Heb. shaked off

verses.text_plain: To him which led his people through the wilderness: for his mercy endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html: 16To him which led his people through the wilderness: for his mercy endureth for ever.

verses.text_plain: To him which smote great kings: for his mercy endureth for ever:
verses.verse_html: 17To him which smote great kings: for his mercy endureth for ever:

verses.text_plain: And slew famous kings: for his mercy endureth for ever:
verses.verse_html: 18And slew famous kings: for his mercy endureth for ever:

verses.text_plain: Sihon king of the Amorites: for his mercy endureth for ever:
verses.verse_html: 19Sihon king of the Amorites: for his mercy endureth for ever:

verses.text_plain: And Og the king of Bashan: for his mercy endureth for ever:
verses.verse_html: 20And Og the king of Bashan: for his mercy endureth for ever:

verses.text_plain: And gave their land for an heritage: for his mercy endureth for ever:
verses.verse_html: 21And gave their land for an heritage: for his mercy endureth for ever:

verses.text_plain: Even an heritage unto Israel his servant: for his mercy endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html: 22Even an heritage unto Israel his servant: for his mercy endureth for ever.

verses.text_plain: Who remembered us in our low estate: for his mercy endureth for ever:
verses.verse_html: 23Who remembered us in our low estate: for his mercy endureth for ever:

verses.text_plain: And hath redeemed us from our enemies: for his mercy endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html: 24And hath redeemed us from our enemies: for his mercy endureth for ever.

verses.text_plain: Who giveth food to all flesh: for his mercy endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html: 25Who giveth food to all flesh: for his mercy endureth for ever.

verses.text_plain: O give thanks unto the God of heaven: for his mercy endureth for ever.
verses.verse_html: 26O give thanks unto the God of heaven: for his mercy endureth for ever.
